  "title": "Project Manager (Facilities Development)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a local leading player in healthcare industry. They are now recruiting a Project Manager to be part of their Facilities Development team to assist the next phase of their business. They are located in the Central-West - easily accessible.</strong></p><p>Roles and Responsibilities of Project Manager:</p><ul><li>Plan and develop healthcare infrastructure facilities</li><li>Manage projects from proposal stage through to completion</li><li>Prepare master plans and budget proposals</li><li>Conduct conceptual planning and feasibility studies</li><li>Oversee design development and coordination</li><li>Prepare and evaluate tender documents</li><li>Supervise construction activities and ensure project delivery</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Min Degree in Architecture</li><li>Experience in facilities development projects in healthcare industry</li><li>Proficient in Autocad drawings</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><p>Email Address: <strong>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p><p>Recruitpedia Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9682</p><p>EA Personnel No: R2198636 (Oh Puey Xin)</p>",
